OL,5,Csays Badenoch
OL,7,FMore than 700 branch managers were
OL,8,Fprosecuted by the Post Office between
OL,9,F1999 and 2015 after faulty Horizon
OL,10,Faccounting software made it look as
OL,11,Fthough money was missing from their
OL,12,Fbranches.
OL,14,FHundreds of subpostmasters and
OL,15,Fsubpostmistresses are still awaiting
OL,16,Fcompensation despite the Government
OL,17,Fannouncing that those who have had
OL,18,Fconvictions quashed are eligible for
OL,19,F#600,000 payouts.
